  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1791934/" class="title-link">勉强算是读完了，消化完估计要很久很久了。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1791934"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kahrpba2100/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1466127-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kahrpba2100/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">琥珀千秋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-03-04"
      class="main-meta">2009-03-04 19:54:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1791934_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  内容非常棒，对于经堂教育不熟悉的读者来说是一次很好的享受之旅。 但是内容上还有不成熟之处，由于引用了非常多的内容，有些细节让人感觉有不完美。 另外书页的质地实在称不上好，手感非常不舒服。  P.S.讨厌那种说本书是针锋时弊的说法，不要将自己的主观臆断加诸别人之上。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1791934/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1791934_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1791934_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3046562">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3046562/" class="title-link">《春秋大义》存疑</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3046562"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/k4StillWell/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2255899-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/k4StillWell/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">空山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-07"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-07 14:31:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3046562_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《春秋大义》是一本很独特的书。从行文风格上来说这是一本结集出版的在网上流传的连载性质的文章。我没有在网上读过。不过读书也很好，因为在网上看这样长的文章难免失之于快餐式阅读的仓促和各种评论的嘈杂。  这是一本很大胆和很用心思考的书。我喜欢这样寻根问底的思想。关...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3046562/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">22有用 / 11没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3046562_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3046562_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
